Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:11.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The rebel,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:15.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hida Takahito.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.26,0:01:18.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotouryuu's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.26,0:01:18.38,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Kyotouryuu = Swordless Style
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.70,0:01:23.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.60,0:01:26.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is how I'll meet my end.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:49.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, it is unavoidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:07.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:10.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in sight now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:16.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of business might you have on an uninhabited island like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:20.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not an uninhabited island.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:23.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the island where the hero of the rebellion was exiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:09.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who came to power after the rebellion, Shogun Yanari, fearing the power of the hero of the rebellion, Yasuri Mutsue,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:14.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,exiled him along with his family to this uninhabited island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:22.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For 20 years after that, no one else stepped foot on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:28.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:29.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Shichika?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:30.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:34.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the cistern's out of water, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:37.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come out dressed like that, it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:38.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.93,0:04:41.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels good if it's just for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:44.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, wasn't it my turn to do the housework today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:45.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:52.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you to stop treating me so delicately?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:54.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't trying to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:55.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:57.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just another part of training.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:05:01.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember teaching you to be overly considerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:04.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,See, go back inside I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:07.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no meaning to training anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:10.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:15.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What meaning is there in maintaining a combat style that will end with your generation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:19.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think about the meaning or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:20.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shichika...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:24.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been a year since father died.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:25.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you let it go already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:27.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to say it like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:31.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, just yesterday, I thought up a new ultimate move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:35.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a really awesome... move...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:40.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To begin with, the one who got banished was father alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:43.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be impossible for me, but you could make a boat for yourself and—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:45.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say stupid stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:50.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't the kind of topic to bring up so early in the morning, was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:56.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll prepare breakfast, so come back quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:57.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:02.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A new ultimate move, you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:03.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Show it to me later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:10.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the island, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:14.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was expecting this topic to come up eventually,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:18.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but this is the only thing I inherited from father, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:22.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to cherish it while I still can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anything else, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:33.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:37.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If father was around he'd cut them down with one strike, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.23,0:06:48.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:01.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A person from the mainland?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:04.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,First time seeing one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.93,0:07:07.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:09.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,First time seeing that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:15.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't personally mind if strangers or outsiders come here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:17.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:21.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's absolutely forbidden to carry blades onto this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:23.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.68,0:07:26.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:27.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:29.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:31.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wasn't the one who decided it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.69,0:07:33.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you come to this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,By boat, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:38.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I particularly wanted to know,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.51,0:07:41.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm supposed to say that in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:42.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:44.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"What did you come here for?" right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:46.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:46.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:53.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that the 6th generation Kyotouryuu head, Yasuri Mutsue lives here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:54.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:56.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're talking about dad, he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:07:58.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:03.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:10.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now I'm the family head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:14.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The 7th generation Kyotouryuu head, Yasuri Shichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:16.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:19.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse my insensitivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:24.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My information was 20 years old, so I had considered he may have passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:25.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:27.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a strong body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:30.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look terrible either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:33.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say it gets a passing grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:34.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:36.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, just talking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:39.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you had business with dad... sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:42.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, but a little off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:44.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My business is with the Kyotouryuu head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:51.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means the business I had with Mutsue-dono has now changed to business with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:57.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichika, I haven't told you my own name yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:08:58.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Togame.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:00.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Togame?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.24,0:09:01.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:10.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In my position as general director for the army of the Shogunate, I serve as a strategist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:14.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll first of all be putting Kyotouryuu to the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.69,0:09:23.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an early work of Mibu Kasamaro, one of the 36 Fugaku swordsmiths.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:24.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Test?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:25.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:26.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:37.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuri Shichika and Togame the strategian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:41.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The unfortunate meeting that began their destiny together,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:48.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,took place in the middle of January, in a time when the word "gyafun" was not yet outdated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:52.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:02.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you're Togame the strategian, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:08.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As you're our first visitor to this island, I'm not entirely sure how to welcome you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:09.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:12.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me for arriving here unannounced.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:15.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Yasuri Mutsue's daughter, Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:20.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you came to visit my father, but what connection do you have with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:23.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really have any "connection" to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:24.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:25.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:29.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can think of me as someone who just got involved, Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:32.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep your sword in my care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:36.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's forbidden to bring or use blades on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:38.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of Kyotouryuu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:44.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's written as "flow of the empty sword", {TL note:　虚刀流 = empty sword flow}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:47.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,a hidden style that uses no sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:50.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones who have openly demonstrated that style,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:52.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,were the first generation head Yasuri Kazuni...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:55.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and the 6th generation head Yasuri Mutsue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:11:01.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When the whole country was plunged into rebellion, it was used in the midst of the chaotic battlefields, the deadliest of sword styles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:08.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That man is the 7th head.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.86,0:11:10.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Togame-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:13.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You tried to attack my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:17.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to see Kyotouryuu in action.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:20.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not used to that sort of thing though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:22.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a strategian, not a swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:24.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was still pretty impressive, given that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:27.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I practiced that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:29.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you keep practicing till you master it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.09,0:11:31.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a rather violent method, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:35.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's understandable if you see it that way, but I had my reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:40.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd heard of the name Yasuri Mutsue, but I don't know his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:42.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be big problem if I got the wrong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:47.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If he demonstrated Kyotouryuu, that would be more convincing than any name could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:51.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Mutsue were Shichika, it'd be the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:53.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, why don't you test him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:57.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Consider yourself lucky to have tripped over that rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:12:03.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If your blade had reached Shichika's body, you wouldn't have escaped with just a bump on your forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:05.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:08.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll accept those words as proof of Kyotouryuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:11.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.88,0:12:14.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hear what you have to say then. {お話を伺いましょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:15.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:17.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, wouldn't you like to rule the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:18.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:19.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:23.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a natural desire for all who live in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:25.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no shame in having ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:29.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who can deny the motivations of rebels?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:34.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you look into it, you'll find that even the current Shogunate were originally servants who supplanted their masters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:36.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means... wait, you said "no"??
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:37.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:39.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:41.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:42.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Togame-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:46.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Being born and raised on this island, we don't really know about the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:50.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better if you assume we don't understand wordy language.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:51.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:55.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, could I have you leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:57.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't agree to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:59.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two reasons why.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.33,0:13:02.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The first is that Kyotouryuu is an art inherited by blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:07.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if dad were still here, he'd have let us stay too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:10.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And the other reason is because I'm bad at thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:14.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You're bad at thinking, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:17.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll continue under the promise of confidentiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:20.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know a swordsmith by the name of Shikizaki Kiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:20.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:22.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.37,0:13:29.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even on this isolated island, any swordsman will at least have heard that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:34.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For a school like Kyotouryuu which fights without weapons, someone like Shikizaki is a natural enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:36.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you said, "no"??
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:37.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:39.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I get the idea that he's a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.99,0:13:41.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikizaki Kiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:45.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall, he was a famous swordsmith from the Sengoku period?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:47.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you know about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:52.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I only heard that he had a close connection to the founder of Kyotouryuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.54,0:13:57.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikizaki didn't belong to any sword school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:14:01.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He isolated himself from others, the most heretic of the heretical swordsmiths.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.41,0:14:06.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it's said his swordsmithery dominated the Sengoku period.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:07.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dominated the Sengoku period?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand the meaning of those words...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:17.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Belonging to no country or house, he distributed the swords he made indiscriminately throughout the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:20.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Within 25 countries, he gave out a thousand swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:21.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A thousand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:22.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:23.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not very many.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:26.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not many then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:31.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The more of his swords a country had, the better they did on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:33.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's not dominating the Sengoku period then what is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:36.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you say it's the other way around?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:42.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Being large and powerful enough to hold an advantage in combat allowed some countries to amass more of his swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:46.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that's how it must look from a practical standpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:50.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, it's also true there's a basis for that myth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:54.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They say 150 years ago, Shogun Kyuu obsessed over those mythical weapons,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:15:00.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and when he achieved unification of the country, he held a majority of the swords, 507 of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:02.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How childish...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.44,0:15:10.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, Shogun Kyuu, who put all his trust in Shikizaki's swords, made that corrupt decree to collect up all swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:12.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The one he said was for making a Buddha statue or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:14.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was only the face of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:18.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the real purpose of it was to bring together all the swordsmen into one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:20.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the true goal was—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:23.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"to collect together all of Shikizaki's swords"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:24.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:26.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite surprising to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:31.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That said, Shogun Kyuu collected over 100,000 swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:33.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,100,000 swords?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:33.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not very many!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:35.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:38.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a lot then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:42.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So did he collect all of Shikizaki's swords?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:43.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:46.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He gave up at the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:51.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He managed to track down the locations of all one thousand swords...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:53.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but only their locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:55.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't he have been able to collect them all then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.49,0:15:57.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He had the authority of the Shogunate after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:16:00.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't work out that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.03,0:16:07.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Among the thousand, the final 12 remaining were incredibly unique. {どうしようもない際物　that right?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:14.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's currently believed that the first 988 were mere practice for the purpose of creating those 12 swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.02,0:16:15.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A thousand for the sake of 12?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:18.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty crazy story, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:19.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:19.79,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Plane, the Absolute
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:20.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Namakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:20.95,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Blunt, the Decapitator
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:22.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsurugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:22.12,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Blade, the Thousand
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:23.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:23.25,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Needle, the Light
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:24.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoroi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:24.42,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Armor, the Grudge
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:25.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanazuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:25.58,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Hammer, the Pair
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:26.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bita.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:26.75,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor, the Evil
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:27.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:27.92,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Sai, the Tiny
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:29.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nokogiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:29.09,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Saw, the King
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:30.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakari.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:30.25,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Scales, the True
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:31.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mekki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:31.42,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Gild, the Poison
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.66,0:16:32.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Jyuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.66,0:16:32.67,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Gun, the Flame
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:39.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The evilness of those swords is incomparable to any other famous sword you've heard of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:45.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The records say that the armies sent by Shogun Kyuu to collect them were wiped out by the power of a single sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:47.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:51.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is why I've come to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:54.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotouryuu head, Yasuri Shichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:17:01.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to convey this command to you, to gather the last 12 swords that the legendary swordsmith Shikizaki Kiki made.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.11,0:17:03.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what you meant when you asked if I wanted to rule the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:04.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:08.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't actually mean you would rule the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:12.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shogunate right now has been stable for a long time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.39,0:17:16.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They had the power to suppress the rebellion with brute force.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:18.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, with brute force...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.84,0:17:23.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No I mean, that rebellion was a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:26.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Owari Shogunate has been in power for 150 years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:30.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No one in this generation really understands what the Sengoku period was like anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:36.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,These days no one really thinks of Shikizaki Kiki's swords as anything more than trinkets, but just think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.35,0:17:41.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If the conspirators behind the last rebellion had gotten a hold of those 12 swords,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.27,0:17:43.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,what would have happened to the current Shogunate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:45.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They fear a revolt...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:47.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"You can never be too careful" kind of thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:49.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So where are those swords currently?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:55.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones we know of are in Inaba, Izumo, Satsuma, Ezo, and Tosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:57.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest are still under investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:00.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You only know half of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:02.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Say "you've already found half of them" instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:03.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.07,0:18:08.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're afraid of a revolt, wouldn't it be smarter not to provoke the current owners?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:12.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Do it skillfully" was the order given by the Shogunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:14.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What does doing it skillfully mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:16.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a strategian for that very purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.54,0:18:19.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who can move about in the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:20.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.52,0:18:22.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is a "strategian"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:31.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Specifically, I'm the army general director in support of critical tasks under direct control of Yanari Shogun of the Owari Shogunate,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.83,0:18:33.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,the strategian Togame.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.49,0:18:35.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:40.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a new post that was created in the last 20 years or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:43.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just made up that title.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:44.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Self-named...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:48.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If tactics are created by a tactician, strategies are created by a strategian!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:51.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm abnormal, so abnormal orders are given to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:56.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That being the case, can you lend me your strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:19:01.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're really from the Shogunate, there's no need for you to rely on Kyotouryuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:04.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you're trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:06.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I can't use people who will work for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:10.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The ninja who were entrusted the task of collecting the swords...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:11.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,betrayed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:13.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they're ninja?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:15.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your surprise is understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:20.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If they did that, the trust in them that they'd built up over all those years would collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:24.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, once they found the swords, they disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:26.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire ninja army, along with their whole village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.84,0:19:28.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:33.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The perfected Deviant Blades are such a high class treasure that you could buy an entire country with the cost of a single sword. {need to standardize 完成形変体刀...}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:35.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why people who'd work for money are unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:37.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:39.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about honor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.18,0:19:42.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My father taught me that swordsmen should do what's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:43.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Honor, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.94,0:19:45.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Swordsmen are no good either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:51.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shogunate picked one of their strongest, most loyal and honorable swordsmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.88,0:19:53.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,His name was Sabi Hakuhei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:58.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They tasked him with retrieving what they thought was hardest sword to obtain - Hakutou Hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.12,0:20:00.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, he obtained it in a shockingly short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.68,0:20:01.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:03.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He obtained it, then disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:04.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:06.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Its poison is too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:12.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And he betrayed us precisely because of that honor — he was unable to resist the honor of owning one of Shikizaki's sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:14.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja and swordsmen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:17.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So the swords are now in the possession of really strong guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:19.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your followers must all be running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.29,0:20:20.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:21.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.64,0:20:22.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'd know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:24.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you sought out Kyotouryuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:28.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Swordsmen who don't work for money nor wield swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:29.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:32.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotouryuu head, Yasuri Shichika!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:36.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to ensure the prosperity of the Owari Shogunate, will you wield the skills you have forged?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:39.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand what you came for,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:44.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and it sounds urgent for you, but I don't have any interest in swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.40,0:20:45.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.41,0:20:46.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:51.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But more importantly, it's a hassle, leaving the island and crossing the sea and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:56.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I didn't anticipate that answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:20:59.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you believe that this strategian who has been betrayed so many times in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:04.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,came to this island without preparing an appropriate reason for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:06.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been betrayed, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.61,0:21:08.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well do you have one? A reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:10.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:12.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,People who work for money are no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:14.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,People who work for honor are also no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:17.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That leaves only one reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.94,0:21:18.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:20.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Love?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:23.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,People who work for love can be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:24.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuri Shichika...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:26.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,fall for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.72,0:21:48.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuriken?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:50.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.27,0:21:52.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the home dad built!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:51.45,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichika...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.21,0:21:57.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, so hasty...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.45,0:21:59.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that was the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.55,0:22:02.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For aerial weaponry, you have to make split-second decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.69,0:22:05.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's just moving on instinct...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.75,0:22:08.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A ninja... from the Maniwa corps, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.61,0:22:10.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maniwa?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:14.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who turned traitor the instant they learned of the value of Shikizaki's swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.08,0:22:15.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How many are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.47,0:22:16.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.84,0:22:20.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maniwa shinobi hate working in groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.53,0:22:24.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What I don't know is why they're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.31,0:22:27.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't tailed, and I didn't tell anyone my destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.95,0:22:30.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If the enemy is really here alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.17,0:22:34.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,then Shichika is probably leading them to the beach ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.73,0:22:36.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem pretty confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.64,0:22:38.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is from the Maniwa corps, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.64,0:22:41.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotouryuu won't lose to a mere ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.71,0:22:48.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's reassuring, but what's most important right now is why is a Maniwa corps soldier is on the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.82,0:22:50.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.61,0:22:54.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Togame-san, are you certain there was no possibility you were followed?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.59,0:22:55.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't insult me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:23:00.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was precisely because the opponent is a ninja that I was more cautious than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.07,0:23:03.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's also why I didn't tell anyone my destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.18,0:23:05.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wonder how...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.89,0:23:09.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to this island alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.20,0:23:10.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're seriously asking that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.78,0:23:13.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get here then?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.03,0:23:14.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I came by boat, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:16.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you row the boat yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.13,0:23:18.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a strange question.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.61,0:23:20.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My specialty is brain work.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.88,0:23:22.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it look like I'd have the strength to—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.19,0:23:24.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So there was a ferryman?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:27.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.03,0:23:27.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.98,0:23:30.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That man wields one of Shikizaki's swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.73,0:23:38.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you're not thinking you've driven me into a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.69,0:23:40.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the opposite!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.18,0:23:42.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who led you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:44.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.97,0:23:48.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My head is spinning from all the visitors here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.12,0:23:50.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you not all come on the same day like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.11,0:23:54.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a damn about your problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.02,0:23:58.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm one of the 12 heads of the Maniwa corps, the great Maniwa Koumori!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.96,0:24:00.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maniwa corps?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.62,0:24:03.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I heard you're a ninja or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.61,0:24:06.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you heard that is bad luck for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.04,0:24:08.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for that, I'd have just ignored you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.84,0:24:12.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My objective is that woman who has all that information.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.92,0:24:14.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were eavesdropping?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.73,0:24:16.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a distasteful hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.05,0:24:18.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You should say it's a good hobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:21.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You tailed Togame here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.72,0:24:22.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.55,0:24:24.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything so sneaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.85,0:24:26.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We came here together.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.27,0:24:28.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I rowed the boat all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.95,0:24:30.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was hard work you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.66,0:24:34.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman just sat on her ass the whole time without lifting a finger to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.53,0:24:38.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Does everyone from the mainland talk as much as this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.79,0:24:37.49,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got quite the nerve, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.03,0:24:39.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.39,0:24:39.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.86,0:24:42.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a pretty dull guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.83,0:24:44.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you are from the boonies I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.87,0:24:46.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't help that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.53,0:24:52.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing personal, but I'll have to kill you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.59,0:24:56.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, this is my first real battle, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.05,0:24:57.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.72,0:24:58.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.80,0:25:01.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking you aren't carrying a sword, as far as I can tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.55,0:25:04.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, you're a swordsman who doesn't use a sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.87,0:25:09.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to "swordsmanship" you usually assume you're going to be fighting with swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.55,0:25:13.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some ridiculously absurd swordsmanship!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.27,0:25:17.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really, it's just that I don't know much about how ninja fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.28,0:25:18.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.60,0:25:23.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,While I'm not a swordsman, it's not like I can't use a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.23,0:25:28.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish, how about I bring out the sword I'm carrying?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.21,0:25:35.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.01,0:25:44.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans can do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.77,0:25:47.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen and look in shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.88,0:25:54.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is one of the 12 Deviant Blades that Shikizaki Kiki perfected, Zettou Kanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.04,0:25:58.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm more shocked at your body than the sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.43,0:26:01.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They call me Hades Koumori!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.54,0:26:06.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning, I have a very generous personality when it comes to serving up presents from hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.58,0:26:08.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Koumori the maid? {TL note: "Hell" sounds like "maid"}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.58,0:26:10.21,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: "Hell" sounds like "maid".
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.21,0:26:10.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds strangely cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.21,0:26:13.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop spouting that nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.19,0:26:16.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, aren't you feeling anything right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.03,0:26:20.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is one of the Shikizaki swords that that woman was talking about earlier, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.28,0:26:22.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.54,0:26:26.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really want to take it when it's all sticky like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.82,0:26:28.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really valuable, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.12,0:26:30.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Should you really be carrying it around like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.44,0:26:32.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.04,0:26:36.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't keep it stored inside my body, I'd be worried about the safety of such a valuable treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.06,0:26:39.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, this thing has an interesting power.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.89,0:26:43.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman called it poison, but this thing is the ultimate medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.77,0:26:46.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When you hold it, you feel its desire to cut off people's heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.25,0:26:48.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Houfuku Zettou! {報復絶刀}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.25,0:26:48.83,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Absolute Retribution Strike
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.05,0:26:58.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotouryuu, first dance: Lily of the Valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.97,0:27:01.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.71,0:27:07.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Houfuku Zettou!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.56,0:27:08.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotouryuu: Chrysanthemum!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.44,0:27:12.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.74,0:27:14.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.44,0:27:15.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw through—
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.19,0:27:16.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so noisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.07,0:27:21.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.74,0:27:25.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time since I've been surprised at anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.11,0:27:27.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You use your arms and legs as swords...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.25,0:27:30.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know your stuff, I guess you really are a swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.40,0:27:33.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not nearly as surprising as you though.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.74,0:27:35.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.13,0:27:37.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,as surprising as that "Kanna".
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.06,0:27:40.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you notice anything from that attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.15,0:27:43.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The technique I just used isn't meant to catch swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.75,0:27:47.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotouryuu: Chrysanthemum is a technique that breaks your opponent's sword in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.90,0:27:50.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That sword is definitely weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.54,0:27:54.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.04,0:27:55.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it's weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.26,0:27:57.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If would be strange if it didn't seem weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.73,0:28:02.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This Zettou Kanna was created with toughness as its main focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.28,0:28:07.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Swords are expendable, so when you use them they'll break or bend and lose their ability to cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.26,0:28:09.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this Kanna is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.28,0:28:11.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't ever be broken or bent.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.66,0:28:14.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it always cuts so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.35,0:28:15.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.32,0:28:20.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's a straight sword, no matter what you do it doesn't chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.16,0:28:23.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Japanese sword that wouldn't break even if elephants trampled it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.40,0:28:25.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd sell for a really high price too!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.64,0:28:28.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I did some research and found out...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.27,0:28:35.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though that Shikizaki geezer was a swordsmith, he also dabbled in the occult and alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.93,0:28:38.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather suspicious methods, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.84,0:28:42.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A guy who pulls swords out of his mouth like you is 12 times more suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.99,0:28:46.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a reason for that little story.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.26,0:28:50.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You must now understand that Kyotouryuu cannot match up to Shikizaki's swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.40,0:28:53.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sword-breaking technique couldn't break it after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.58,0:28:57.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see that Kyotouryuu aims to destroy the opponent's weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.59,0:28:59.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, that's outstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.43,0:29:02.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have loved to see you do it though!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.36,0:29:07.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotouryuu, second dance: Daffodil.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.74,0:29:12.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This time I will definitely shatter that Zettou Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.34,0:29:13.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.53,0:29:19.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean shatter it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.93,0:29:23.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I brought it like that to the Shogunate, they'd make me commit harakiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.15,0:29:23.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.90,0:29:27.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you listen to a single word I was saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.28,0:29:32.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I said I'd accept your request anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.15,0:29:33.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the problem here!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.97,0:29:36.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand the value of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.38,0:29:37.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.96,0:29:43.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As one who understands the value of things, smashing something of monetary worth is unthinkable to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.88,0:29:44.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.72,0:29:48.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about I start off with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.74,0:29:50.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, little kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.88,0:29:52.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maniwa Koumori...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.74,0:29:54.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.34,0:29:58.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja may be traitors, but sneakiness is our selling point. {卑怯卑劣が売りなんだから。}{sneaky cowardice is our selling point?}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.90,0:29:59.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.77,0:30:04.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have plenty of time to talk about that later, Miss strategian.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.27,0:30:07.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice and slowly, after I destroy this Kyotouryuu guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.24,0:30:09.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichika, defeat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.25,0:30:12.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, that Kanna has got me riled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.28,0:30:14.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, don't break it!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.41,0:30:15.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.95,0:30:18.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have any other requests, say so now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.06,0:30:19.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to end this right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.71,0:30:21.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.59,0:30:24.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If at all possible, do it with a flashy move.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.55,0:30:29.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to hand in a report describing how we obtained the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.28,0:30:34.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have some cool move that'll capture the reader's attention, I'll ask that you use it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.91,0:30:38.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, don't destroy that sword, even accidentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.25,0:30:41.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, this story will end at chapter one!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.70,0:30:44.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Chapter one? Are you writing a book?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.23,0:30:46.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd also like to do that sometime in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.43,0:30:48.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd sell!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.14,0:30:50.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll show you something flashy then.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.24,0:30:51.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Koumori.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.78,0:30:52.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.45,0:30:58.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No no, it was me delaying this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.32,0:30:59.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.56,0:31:01.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not going to be much of a fight like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.87,0:31:02.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.77,0:31:04.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a swordsman, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.88,0:31:08.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm particular about this sword, so being beaten by you here wouldn't be very shinobi of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.88,0:31:08.55,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: "shinobi" also means "to steal"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.56,0:31:10.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, was that a pun?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.92,0:31:12.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.10,0:31:13.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat you either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.10,0:31:17.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no match for me if I fight with ninjutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.68,0:31:20.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My actual battlefield experience is on a different level from yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.32,0:31:23.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So far this has just been a welcoming reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.25,0:31:26.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think of it as a bad habit of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.95,0:31:28.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be serious from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.63,0:31:30.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.05,0:31:33.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing isn't just a decoration for you to get your drool all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.33,0:31:35.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it out! Take it out right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.86,0:31:39.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, such a noisy little kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.28,0:31:40.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.57,0:31:42.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're unexpectedly cooperati—
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.17,0:31:54.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.29,0:32:01.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.86,0:32:07.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, that was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.21,0:32:10.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That kid is really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.16,0:32:13.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I was expecting something like that, little kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.94,0:32:25.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.03,0:32:26.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.86,0:32:29.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'll be killing you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.93,0:32:30.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Koumori!!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.59,0:32:34.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably think you've found something good,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.20,0:32:35.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but that's too naive!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.40,0:32:38.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He may be used to battling, but he's never been on a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.60,0:32:40.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a coward who runs away.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.33,0:32:43.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey, what are you blabbing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.39,0:32:48.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't a wise person supposed to fight strength using intellect, Miss strategian?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.13,0:32:51.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All you do is bully weaker people!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.02,0:32:57.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I come up with strategies that allow the weak to challenge the strong, by whittling away their life and spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.47,0:32:59.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even compare us, you lowlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.06,0:33:01.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see strategians are also good at running their mouths off.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.87,0:33:03.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though even so, that's not what you did, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.94,0:33:04.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.71,0:33:06.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fall for me"?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.30,0:33:09.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, that's pretty wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.06,0:33:12.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so surprised I accidentally spat out those shuriken.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.64,0:33:15.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That attack wasn't intentional?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.00,0:33:17.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was way too embarrassing for me to bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.02,0:33:23.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's touching, I'd have liked someone to say that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.79,0:33:27.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well I overheard all the information I needed, so it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.55,0:33:29.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.01,0:33:32.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop trying to act so dignified, little kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.13,0:33:37.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even while you say that, you're trying to think of a way to outsmart me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.76,0:33:41.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're even more tricky than me. {totally not what he says. help. あんたの腹の中は、俺以上に混沌としてるぜ}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.32,0:33:44.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.83,0:33:48.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I deliberately missed with that shuriken attack earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.42,0:33:51.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand the concept of moderation do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.78,0:33:54.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If one had even nicked me, I would have died! {nicked? glanced? hit? かすったりしようものなら、わたしは絶対に死んでいたぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.83,0:33:56.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know how fragile I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.92,0:33:59.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not something you should be bragging about!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.85,0:34:03.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll torture you when I return, so bear with it a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.22,0:34:07.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you're not completely clueless about the location of the remaining swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.72,0:34:09.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though since this is the end I guess I'll ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.74,0:34:13.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about turning your back on the Shogunate and following us?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.19,0:34:15.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure to give you a piece of the action.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.37,0:34:16.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.32,0:34:18.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,People who work for money can't be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.74,0:34:20.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're afraid of being betrayed?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.65,0:34:23.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say it's more strange to trust in a ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.39,0:34:25.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.20,0:34:33.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you've been thinking it, but the truth is you're not actually a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.61,0:34:35.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.26,0:34:39.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I changed my appearance to that of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.52,0:34:55.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This way even that Kyotouryuu guy will let down his guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.57,0:34:59.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be aware of my ability, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.10,0:35:02.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I found Kanna under your orders, then stole it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.97,0:35:12.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After I kill that Kyotouryuu guy, maybe I'll transform into him to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.24,0:35:16.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'll have you wait there until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.19,0:35:16.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.96,0:35:19.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I originally betrayed you for money,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.36,0:35:24.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but even were it not for that, if i had known what kind of person you were from the start, I wouldn't have worked with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.78,0:35:27.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even that invitation just now was just so I could work with you again,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.01,0:35:31.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and then betray you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.44,0:35:36.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one in this world who'd stay by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.65,0:35:42.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.43,0:35:49.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where on earth did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.44,0:35:53.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the island, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.91,0:35:54.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This late...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.88,0:35:57.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.98,0:36:06.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that Kyotouryuu is a particularly troublesome opponent against Shikizaki's Deviant Blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.52,0:36:09.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to make use of this chance to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.04,0:36:12.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead for sure. It's too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.59,0:36:17.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, once that woman set her eyes on him, his luck had already run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.00,0:36:18.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.31,0:36:24.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The premise is I barely escaped with my life from captivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.04,0:36:26.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Before he can say anything, embrace him...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.26,0:36:27.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And then kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.54,0:36:31.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichika!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.61,0:36:42.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotouryuu: Peony!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.61,0:36:45.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.76,0:36:50.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What was wrong? The disguise?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.10,0:36:53.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this isn't even a disguise, my transformation was perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.96,0:36:57.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I look, it's Togame?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.73,0:36:58.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.67,0:37:00.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He used that technique without even knowing who I was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.61,0:37:01.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.79,0:37:04.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, then I guess you're Koumori?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.27,0:37:05.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.06,0:37:06.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.62,0:37:08.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you even recognize who you're facing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.83,0:37:13.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, today's the first time I've ever seen another human besides Nee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.10,0:37:14.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't recognize faces that quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.58,0:37:16.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.10,0:37:17.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This wasn't even a question of disguise!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.49,0:37:20.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,From the beginning, this guy couldn't even differentiate between people?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.36,0:37:21.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.67,0:37:23.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was her, she'd have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.21,0:37:26.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is beyond boonies...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.12,0:37:27.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's an animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.59,0:37:30.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She asked for a flashy move, but it turned out kind of boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.70,0:37:32.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.57,0:37:35.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really want to help that woman so badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.82,0:37:37.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking if you want to be used by her!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.81,0:37:38.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Used?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.47,0:37:42.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you think there was something strange about her story?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.43,0:37:45.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does the Shogunate suddenly want to collect Shikizaki's swords after all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.94,0:37:48.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was... because they fear a revolt?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.14,0:37:50.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That is indeed a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.99,0:37:52.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.37,0:37:56.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,don't you think it sounds too convenient?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.84,0:38:01.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shogunate today doesn't hold the same reverence for Shikizaki's swords as Shogun Kyuu did.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.54,0:38:03.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're far more pragmatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.13,0:38:09.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimately, collecting up the swords this time is just a means for that woman to gain recognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.17,0:38:11.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Togame the strategian...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.06,0:38:16.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing but a move on her part to gain fame within the army as general director.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.89,0:38:19.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand that recognition stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.61,0:38:23.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but isn't general director of the army already pretty high up? {fix 軍所総監督って時点で、そこそこ偉いんじゃないのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.07,0:38:25.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman isn't happy with that level.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.93,0:38:27.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's aiming for the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.44,0:38:29.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know what it means to doubt someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.39,0:38:34.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That young woman will use any dirty tactics she needs to rise to the top of the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.97,0:38:37.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Raw strength isn't everything in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.98,0:38:40.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When we first met, she terrified me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.61,0:38:42.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There is ambition in her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.84,0:38:46.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can sense her willingness to sacrifice anyone and anything for her goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.22,0:38:48.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She was perfectly willing to use the Maniwa corps, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.93,0:38:53.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A fearsome ninja brigade made up of professional assassins, you know? Madness!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.76,0:38:56.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And she is merely using you too, Kyotouryuu head!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.13,0:38:59.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it going to end here?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.41,0:39:01.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.79,0:39:04.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So before you were betrayed, you betrayed others?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.27,0:39:05.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.19,0:39:07.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'd follow that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.72,0:39:10.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think her ultimate aim lies?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.90,0:39:12.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The right hand of the Shogun!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.45,0:39:15.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The current Shogun is getting old.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.76,0:39:17.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be long before he retires.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.80,0:39:23.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens, I'm sure you can imagine what the natural step will be for the young lieutenant at his side?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.75,0:39:24.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruling the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.88,0:39:29.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I threw away my name and my family, all for it to end on this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.99,0:39:33.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not really something to condemn her for...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.34,0:39:38.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, for someone like you who was used, I'm sure it doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.30,0:39:40.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really care about being used.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.23,0:39:42.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Being used and using others is the way of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.34,0:39:47.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, my problem in this case is the reason I was used!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.14,0:39:51.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In case you don't know, my head isn't that great, so saying stuff like that doesn't really get through to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.21,0:39:57.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman is the daughter of the leader of the last rebellion, Hida Takahito!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.54,0:40:01.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who can deny the motivations of rebels?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.96,0:40:05.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If things had gone better, she'd have been the princess in her castle, ruling over a whole country.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.63,0:40:07.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can already see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.11,0:40:09.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's within my grasp!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.55,0:40:13.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman is aiming for promotion without a care for the means.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.14,0:40:15.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She aims to be the right hand man to the current Shogun.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.90,0:40:17.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you understand what that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.95,0:40:19.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Father's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.79,0:40:21.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Father's regrets...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.10,0:40:25.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She was willing to ask for help from her father's enemies to collect those swords?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.86,0:40:29.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be clear to you by now what she's planning...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.26,0:40:30.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.74,0:40:33.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have been able to avenge father's death!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.66,0:40:37.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's revenge for having her whole family exterminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.86,0:40:43.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, that girl was watching as her family was killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.80,0:40:53.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that was the only possibility, to ask the person responsible for my father's death...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.97,0:40:56.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if not that, to depend on his son...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.92,0:40:58.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm the son of her enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.42,0:41:02.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I was wrong to rely on Kyotouryuu after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.14,0:41:05.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's an insect born from the leader of the rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.90,0:41:11.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear about treachery or cowardice from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.07,0:41:14.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a good body.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.52,0:41:16.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to use it as a reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.35,0:41:20.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your strength, musculature, and balance are all a perfect fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.43,0:41:22.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.63,0:41:28.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,you've got the pain from when my shuriken hit your arms and legs, so I have a bit of an advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.75,0:41:32.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, an attack like that doesn't hurt or even itch anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.43,0:41:37.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems it, so I guess we're as equal as rock vs rock. {ie: rock-paper-scissors}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.79,0:41:41.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though my "rock" here is quite strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.16,0:41:42.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.67,0:41:46.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anyone else who knows Togame's secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.30,0:41:49.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'd just give away such intriguing information.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.51,0:41:52.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So it'll be fine if I just finish you off here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.27,0:41:56.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're suddenly in a fighting mood now that you're facing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.76,0:42:01.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the 7th generation Kyotouryuu head, Yasuri Shichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.49,0:42:02.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go! {推して参る}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.67,0:42:05.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to act cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.29,0:42:07.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.37,0:42:09.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish you with an extremely flashy move!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.75,0:42:11.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate secret technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.63,0:42:14.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Houfuku Zettou!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.39,0:42:21.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.51,0:42:25.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotouryuu men don't have any skill whatsoever with a sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.77,0:42:27.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not swordsmen who don't use swords,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.98,0:42:29.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,we're swordsmen who {\i1}can't{\i0\fscx166} {\fscx100}use them!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.27,0:42:32.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.28,0:42:35.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, I called it "ultimate secret technique",
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.61,0:42:39.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but the reason it sounds so generic is because it's an ultimate move I only came up with yesterday! {needs fixing for meaning of かってえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.20,0:42:46.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The opponent take 7 hits from this secret technique, getting ripped apart in the blink of an eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.50,0:42:48.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So for now, I'll call it:
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.47,0:43:00.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotouryuu: Shichika Hachiretsu! {TL note: 7 petal 8 fissure}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.85,0:43:12.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a state I'm in now...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.52,0:43:14.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm from a samurai bloodline too!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.32,0:43:16.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Before my appearance becomes any more embarrassing, I've got to...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.40,0:43:21.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like this rope can't loosen or unravel...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.82,0:43:24.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my strategies that are infallible and sharp!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.62,0:43:26.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can lose to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.16,0:43:30.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.09,0:43:36.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the "eye" he was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.47,0:43:42.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To me at least, it sparkles in quite a pretty way.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.89,0:43:47.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well for now, I've got one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.94,0:43:55.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he sound like he's just getting started?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.78,0:44:01.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichika, what about Koumori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.07,0:44:04.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I finished him off with an awesome move.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.32,0:44:05.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.58,0:44:08.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.62,0:44:12.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get me wrong, I did it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.92,0:44:19.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I want money or that I've been lured in by Shikizaki's swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.13,0:44:22.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't have a shred of obligation to help the Shogunate either.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.97,0:44:25.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just decided I want to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.51,0:44:28.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've fallen for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.66,0:44:52.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Togame-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.96,0:44:57.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to let you know I approve of this decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.88,0:44:59.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.21,0:45:00.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought for sure you'd object.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.51,0:45:03.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.13,0:45:08.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well to be honest, I don't really care at all about the actual basis of your journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.85,0:45:14.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If that child has found a reason to leave this island, I approve of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.56,0:45:20.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been on this island for 20 years, training and studying hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.82,0:45:24.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and it'd simply be too much of a waste if he didn't accomplish anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.49,0:45:29.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, it's not going to be any sort of simple journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.74,0:45:36.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's the Maniwa corps and Sabi Hakuhei of course, and on top of that, any other monsters that may lie where we're headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.21,0:45:38.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Demons and serpents...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.13,0:45:41.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bringing along your brother to fight those kinds of battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.80,0:45:44.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite kind, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.97,0:45:48.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You truly care about him, don't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.80,0:45:52.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no worries entrusting him to your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.52,0:45:55.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.10,0:46:00.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not such a kind woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.69,0:46:07.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuri Shichika, I have four directives for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.86,0:46:08.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Four?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.70,0:46:09.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.57,0:46:12.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,First I'll repeat what I said earlier - don't break the swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.37,0:46:13.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.20,0:46:14.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect the swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.96,0:46:15.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The second?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.54,0:46:17.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.17,0:46:21.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though our objective is the collection of Shikizaki's swords, if I die it'll all be in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.71,0:46:22.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.63,0:46:24.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.51,0:46:25.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The third?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.55,0:46:27.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.55,0:46:30.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not me being considerate of you or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.85,0:46:34.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we collect all 12 of Shikizaki's swords, dying is unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.93,0:46:35.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.93,0:46:37.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.89,0:46:38.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The fourth?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.19,0:46:40.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.19,0:46:44.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is me being considerate of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.94,0:46:47.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.11,0:46:50.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The road will be harsh, but you mustn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.20,0:46:51.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.07,0:46:52.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you say you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.49,0:46:54.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and say you get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.79,0:46:56.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I completely understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.83,0:46:57.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.91,0:46:59.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to rush ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.25,0:47:01.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When we get to the city, I'll buy you some clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.13,0:47:02.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.13,0:47:03.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.13,0:47:03.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.88,0:47:06.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Love me as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.97,0:47:11.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A man unknown to anyone, a woman who closed her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.22,0:47:14.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And so those two began their journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.85,0:47:19.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With no destination nor destiny, a journey to collect swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.73,0:47:23.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Demons and serpents await them.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.82,0:47:27.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The story of Katanagatari on this month and this evening...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.74,0:47:29.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.29,0:47:35.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.70,0:47:39.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That child is so weak... will they be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.55,0:49:13.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the army general director in support of critical tasks,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.54,0:49:16.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,under direct control of Yanari Shogun of the Owari Shogunate,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.08,0:49:17.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Togame the strategian here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.21,0:49:20.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is going according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.59,0:49:21.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You doubt me?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.84,0:49:23.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I also calculated you'd think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.51,0:49:25.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.22,0:49:30.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-1}it's time for my peerless, uplifting, solemn story of justice to begin, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.27,0:49:31.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,About that Kyotouryuu man,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.22,0:49:33.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuri Shichika...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.52,0:49:35.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How far will he serve as my blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.23,0:49:38.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Katanagatari - Zantou Namakura
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.73,0:49:39.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheerio!
